game.description:
The biggest fashion festival the Burning Man is just around the corner and four beautiful princesses and best friends are finding it really difficult to carry this style to look fabulous on this occasion. Hey ladies! This is a wonderful opportunity for you as well since they have hired you as their personal stylist. No need to think anymore! All you need to do is just join Princess BFF Burning Man right away and let your inner stylist ability work for these 4 gorgeous ladies. 
Disney princesses Rapunzel and their best friends Selena Gomez and Ariana Grande, who are also the popular celebrities, are ready to hit the Black Rock City in a unique fashionable style. Mix and match as many outfits as you can to give them the statement looks on this occasion in this one of the best HTML5 dressing games for girls! Start this dress-up fun with the princess Rapunzel by checking out her wardrobe closely! Give her a combo of daring bodysuits and pair it with the denims shorts!
Do not forget to accessorize your girl with golden jewelries along with leather boots and a cool faux-fur jacket. Tight bodysuits and colorful outfits are the first choice for Miss Ariana Grande. Selena Gomez is a lover of fitting outfits this summer season. Make sure to dress her up with the colorful prints and combine her outfit with funky sunglasses and an oversized necklace. Spot some of the trendiest clothing items and accessories in the wardrobe of Queen Elsa and dress her with the suitable one! Have a blast alone or with your friends, no download required!
